460" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3763460" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg" alt="比莉·艾利什在舞台上表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/billie-eilish@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3763460" class="wp-caption-text">比莉·艾利什.图片来源：阿图罗·霍姆斯/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>当被问及卡马拉承诺解决的与艾利什有关的问题时，这位年轻的音乐家回答道：“他真的是人权的忠实拥护者。非常支持妇女权利、妇女生殖权利、社会正义和枪支法。我的很多粉丝将能够第一次投票。所以我问，‘你喜欢自由吗？’第一位女总统？真的会很棒。作为一名女性，我希望在自己的国家感到安全。”</p><p>继上个月公开支持哈里斯之后，艾利什的《当派对结束时》最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilishs-when-the-partys-over-closes-kamala-harris-ad-on-reproductive-care-3795331">出现在民主党关于生殖保健的广告中</a>。</p><p>艾利什只是在即将到来的选举中表示支持哈里斯的众多音乐家之一。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">Taylor Swift</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">Charli XCX</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-freedom-soundtracks-kamala-harris-first-presidential-election-campaign-video-3777987">Beyoncé</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-slams-those-avoiding-presidential-election-what-the-fuck-are-you-talking-about-3790934">Megan Thee Stallion</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-pnk-perform-what-about-us-with-daughter-to-close-democratic-national-convention-3786178">P!nk</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">Bon Iver</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/quavo-backs-kamala-harris-for-tackling-gun-violence-at-atlanta-rally-3779672">Quavo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-endorses-kamala-harris-for-us-president-ive-only-got-one-vote-and-its-one-of-the-most-precious-possessions-that-i-have-3799537">Bruce Springsteen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-clears-up-elections-stance-im-voting-for-fucking-kamala-3797165">Chappell Roan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-throws-support-behind-kamala-harris-over-reproductive-rights-stance-3777706">Olivia Rodrigo</a>等艺术家也在今年 11 月的大选前站出来支持哈里斯。 </p><figure id="attachment_3777450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3777450" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3777450" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="卡玛拉·哈里斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3777450" class="wp-caption-text">卡玛拉·哈里斯——图片来源：Andrew Harnik/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Billie Eilish <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-billie-eilish-levitate-in-new-video-for-birds-of-a-feather-3797975">最近分享了《Birds Of A Feather》的音乐视频</a>。这段受超自然启发的视频由艾丹·扎米里 (Aidan Zamiri) 执导，视频中，艾利什 (Eilish) 被无形的力量抓住，将她拖过地板，爬上墙壁。</p><p>在其他消息中，她将与主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-keaton">迈克尔·基顿</a>一起作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/snl-to-kick-off-50th-season-with-coldplay-stevie-nicks-chappell-roan-and-more-3795032">音乐嘉宾出现在 10 月 19 日的<i>《周六夜现场》</i>节目中</a>。最近还有消息称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-is-learning-to-do-home-production-without-finneas-3797325">艾利什现在正在学习“在没有她哥哥芬尼斯的情况下进行家庭制作”</a> ，迄今为止，芬尼斯已经制作了她的全部三张专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-says-she-would-feel-safe-as-a-woman-in-my-country-with-kamala-harris-as-president-3800859">比莉·艾利什 (Billie Eilish) 表示，如果卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 担任总统，她“作为一名女性在我的国家会感到安全”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
新纪录片《公众之敌》探讨肯德里克·拉马尔和德雷克之间的恩怨https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-documentary-public-enemies-to-explore-kendrick-lamar-and-drake-feud-3800851?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=new-documentary-public-敌人探索肯德里克·拉马尔和德雷克的不和Surej SinghWed, 09 Oct 2024 03:39:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsHip-hopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3800851 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该剧将在英国第四频道播出，美国的播出计划尚未公布</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-documentary-public-enemies-to-explore-kendrick-lamar-and-drake-feud-3800851">探讨肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 和德雷克 (Drake) 不和的新纪录片《公众之敌》(Public Enemies)</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kendrick-lamar-drake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一部关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">德雷克</a>今年早些时候爆发性不和的新纪录片已经发布。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/drake-and-kendrick-lamars-feud-the-full-timeline-3754820">德雷克和肯德里克·拉马尔的不和：完整的时间表</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/10/channel-4-kendrick-lamar-draka-public-enemies-doc-1236109090/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Deadline</em></a>报道，英国第四频道已经批准了这部名为<em>《公众之敌：肯德里克 vs 德雷克》</em>的纪录片。上映日期尚未公布，也没有在美国的播出计划。</p><p> <em>《公众之敌：肯德里克 vs 德雷克》</em>将包括档案片段和对与说唱歌手合作过的人的新采访，并将探讨牛肉“如何受到如此普遍的赞誉，同时通过创造他们的当代历史和文化来了解他们的职业生涯。 ”</p><p>这也涉及肯德里克·拉马尔对德雷克恋童癖的指控，他在《认识格雷厄姆一家》和《不像我们》中大量引用了这一指控。 Acme Films 制作了 2017 年纪录片<em>《公众之敌：Jay-Z vs Kanye</em> 》，也将制作《Kendrick vs Drake》项目。 </p><figure id="attachment_3792880" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3792880" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3792880" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1.jpg" alt="肯德里克·拉马尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/kendrick-lamar-not-like-us@2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3792880" class="wp-caption-text">肯德里克·拉马尔在《不像我们》音乐录影带拍摄期间。图片来源：Michael Blackshire / 洛杉矶时报 via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>第四频道的沙米德·纳哈尔 (Shaminder Nahal) 在给<em>Deadline</em>的一份声明中表示：“ <em>《公众之敌：肯德里克 vs 德雷克》</em>不仅仅是一部传记。这是对现代音乐中两个最具影响力的声音的文化探索。这部纪录片将深入探讨肯德里克和德雷克的独特旅程，探讨他们的背景、才能和愿景如何使他们成为全球偶像。”</p><p>今年早些时候，拉马尔和德雷克因持续不断的 diss 曲目而发生争执。当<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-claims-he-fed-kendrick-lamar-false-intel-on-new-diss-the-heart-part-6-3753644">德雷克放弃了他的新diss歌曲“The Heart Part 6”</a>时，这场争执就结束了，这位加拿大说唱歌手在这首歌曲中暗示拉马尔的diss是基于德雷克团队向他提供的虚假信息。他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-denies-paedophile-allegations-in-new-kendrick-lamar-diss-track-3753665">否认肯德里克·拉马尔在《拜见格雷厄姆一家》节目中游说他有恋童癖的指控</a>。</p><p>这场不和源于拉马尔在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/future">《Future》</a>中的诗句和三月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metro-boomin">Metro Boomin</a>的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-takes-aim-at-drake-and-j-cole-on-metro-boomins-like-that-fuck-sneak-dissin-first-person-shooter-3608327">Like That</a> 》。在主歌中，他回应了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-cole">J. Cole</a> ，后者声称<em>“爱当他们争论最难的 MC / 是 K-Dot 吗？”是奥布里吗？还是我？ /我们三巨头就像我们开始了一个联盟一样”</em>在 Drake 的歌曲“第一人称射击游戏”中客串。</p><p> Drake 以两首歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-taunts-kendrick-lamar-says-he-has-nothing-to-drop-in-response-to-push-ups-diss-track-3620086">“Push Ups”</a>和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-taunts-kendrick-lamar-again-with-a-i-2pac-and-snoop-dogg-on-taylor-made-freestyle-3719747">Taylor Made Freestyle</a> ”进行回击。德雷克在后一首歌曲中使用人工智能来模仿<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Tupac-Shakur">图帕克</a>的声音，导致已故说唱歌手的遗产<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tupac-shakurs-estate-threatens-legal-action-against-drake-over-diss-track-using-ai-generated-vocals-3750354">威胁要采取法律行动</a>。随后他从直播中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-removes-diss-track-using-ai-generated-tupac-vocals-after-estate-threatens-lawsuit-3751219">删除了这条diss</a> 。拉马尔随后于 5 月 1 日以“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamars-drake-diss-track-euphoria-features-sample-of-reversed-richard-pryor-line-from-the-wiz-3752511">Euphoria</a> ”进行回应，并在第二天迅速跟进“6:16 in LA”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3762140" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3762140" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3762140" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270.jpg" alt="德雷克现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/drake@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3762140" class="wp-caption-text">德雷克。图片来源：威廉姆斯王子/Wireimage</figcaption></figure><p> Drake 的《The Heart Part 6》是两位说唱歌手之间反复争执的最新一击。在此之前，肯德里克·拉马尔放弃了《不像我们》。前一天，两位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-responds-to-kendrick-lamar-diss-with-family-matters-lamar-drops-meet-the-grahams-an-hour-later-3753494">发布的言论相隔一小时</a>。德雷克发行了《Family Matters》，拉马尔迅速回应了《Meet The Grahams》。</p><p>在其他新闻中，拉马尔最近被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-to-headline-2025-super-bowl-halftime-show-3791716">任命为 2025 年超级碗中场秀的头条表演者</a>：“我不想让你错过它。 2025 年 2 月 9 日在新奥尔良与我见面。即使您在家观看比赛，也请穿上您最好的衣服。我们走吧。”</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kendrick-lamar-surprise-releases-new-single-on-social-media-3792879">最近还在社交媒体上发布了一首新单曲</a>。据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/kendrick-lamar-drops-first-song-since-not-like-us-1236141721/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，该剧尚未登陆任何流媒体平台，据报道标题为“Watch The Party Die”。本周早些时候，有报道称肯德里克<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rihanna-and-kendrick-lamar-reportedly-decline-coachella-2025-headline-slots-3800135">拒绝了明年科切拉音乐节的主唱邀请</a>。</p><p>至于德雷克，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-has-dropped-100-gigabytes-of-data-including-three-new-songs-3781575">在网上分享了价值100GB的数据，其中包括三首新歌</a>。在这三首歌曲中，《It&#39;s Up》是最以说唱为主的一首， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-thug">Young Thug 的</a>Trap 曲目尤为突出。 《Housekeeping Knows》呈现出一种舞蹈氛围，并以<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/latto">Latto</a>为特色，而《Blue Green Red》则是一首较慢的俱乐部曲子，不包含任何特色。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-documentary-public-enemies-to-explore-kendrick-lamar-and-drake-feud-3800851">探讨肯德里克·拉马尔 (Kendrick Lamar) 和德雷克 (Drake) 不和的新纪录片《公众之敌》(Public Enemies)</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
